Package: BMDD
Type: Package
Title: Bimodal Dirichlet distribution (BMDD) for microbiome data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Huijuan Zhou, Lu Yang, Jun Chen, Xianyang Zhang
Maintainer: Huijuan Zhou <huijuanzhou2019@gmail.com>
Description: The function implements a variational EM algorithm for estimating the parameters in bimodal Dirichlet distribution. For the microbiome data, the unobserved true compositions are assumed to follow the bimodal Dirichlet distribution, thus the function also estimates the posterior distribution of the true compositions.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
